    ,Place(name: 'Ocean Basket Ayia Napa', imagePath: 'famagustaRest/ocean.jpg', lat:34.98322597614805, long: 34.00312891391413,id: 1056, city: 'Ayia Napa, Famagusta', category: 'Restaurant, Seafood', url: 'https://cyprus.oceanbasket.com/our-restaurants/ocean-basket-ayia-napa', description: 'Ocean Basket in Agia Napa is a highly acclaimed seafood and sushi restaurant, located at the Agia Napa fishing harbour. It offers a diverse menu with Mediterranean favorites and a selection of sushi, known for generous portions. The restaurant boasts a breezy, open-air sitting area with views of Limanaki and Pantachou beach, as well as an air-conditioned dining hall (photo from Check In Cyprus).' )
   ,Place(name: 'Hungry Horse', imagePath: 'famagustaRest/hungry house.jpg', lat: 34.99164024081334,long: 33.99740203802188,id: 1057, category: 'Restaurant, Seafood', city: 'Ayia Napa, Famagusta', url: 'https://www.facebook.com/hungryhorsetaverna/', description: 'I couldn\'t find a Hungry Horse pub specifically in Ayia Napa or details about traditional food offerings there. However, if such a place existed, it might serve a mix of British pub classics along with local Cypriot cuisine, offering guests a taste of home while abroad and a chance to enjoy local flavors. Imagine enjoying a hearty plate of fish and chips alongside a local meze platter, combining the best of both worlds in a lively, family-friendly setting typical of Hungry Horse establishments.'),
    Place(name: 'Taverna Isaak', imagePath: 'famagustaRest/isaak.jpg', lat:34.98204706686558, long: 34.00133069198278,id: 1058, city: 'Ayia Napa, Famagusta', category: 'Restaurant, Seafood', url: 'https://www.facebook.com/IsaacTavern/', description: 'Taverna Isaak, nestled in the heart of Ayia Napa, is renowned for its exquisite seafood dishes that capture the essence of Mediterranean cuisine. With a focus on fresh catch sourced locally, visitors can indulge in a variety of fish dishes prepared with traditional Cypriot flair. From succulent grilled sea bass drizzled with olive oil and sprinkled with herbs to mouthwatering seafood platters showcasing the best of the sea, Taverna Isaak promises a culinary experience that tantalizes the taste buds and leaves diners longing for more. Whether you\'re a seafood aficionado or simply seeking to savor the flavors of the Mediterranean, Taverna Isaak offers an unforgettable dining experience amidst the charm of Ayia Napa.' )
