  , Place(name: 'McDonald\'s Limassol Germasogia',lat: 34.70022154505467, long: 33.100615243078465, imagePath: 'limassolRest/mcgermassogia.jpg', id: 143, city: 'Limassol', category: 'Fast Food', description: 'McDonald\'s Corporation, an iconic American fast-food chain, was founded in 1940 as a restaurant by Richard and Maurice McDonald in San Bernardino, California, and later transformed into a franchise with the now-famous Golden Arches logo by Ray Kroc in 1955. Headquartered in Chicago, Illinois, it is one of the world\'s largest chains of fast food restaurants, operating over 40,000 locations in more than 100 countries. Renowned for its hamburgers, chicken, french fries, and breakfast items, McDonald\'s is also a significant real estate company, owning or leasing the land for its franchised location (photo from Tripadvisor).', url: 'https://www.mcdonalds.com.cy/' )
    ,Place(name: 'Meze Taverna Restaurant', imagePath: 'limassolRest/meze.jpg', lat: 34.67657191834625, long: 33.047484804038014, city: 'Limassol', id: 144,category: 'Restaurant, Traditional Food', description: 'Meze Taverna Restaurant, located near the Old Port in Limassol, Cyprus, is a family-run establishment renowned for its traditional Cypriot and Greek cuisine. Owned by Diomides and Kicoulla Machlouzarides, who have over 30 years of experience in the restaurant industry, the eatery offers a variety of both meat and fish mezes. Among the popular dishes served are chicken breast skewers, pork kebabs, sheftalia (a homemade sausage), mixed grills, pork chops, and lamb cutlets, all accompanied by rice or chips and a garnish salad (photo from Tripadvisor).', url: 'https://www.mezetaverna.com/'),
    Place(name: 'Pyxida', imagePath: 'limassolRest/pyxida.jpg', lat:34.66956411093809, long: 33.03930071070445, category: 'Restaurant, Seafood',id: 1052, city: 'Limassol', url: 'https://pyxidafishtavern.com/', description: 'Pyxida, located in Limassol Marina, is a haven for seafood enthusiasts seeking a culinary adventure inspired by the Mediterranean. With a focus on showcasing the freshest catch of the day, Pyxida offers an extensive menu featuring a wide array of seafood delicacies. From succulent grilled octopus to exquisite lobster risotto and flavorful fish meze platters, every dish is crafted with precision and passion, highlighting the natural flavors of the sea. The elegant yet relaxed ambiance of Pyxida provides the perfect backdrop for indulging in a seafood feast while enjoying stunning views of the marina. Whether you\'re a connoisseur or an adventurous diner eager to explore the wonders of the sea, Pyxida promises an unforgettable dining experience that celebrates the bounty of the Mediterranean (photo from Check In Cyprus).' ),
    Place(name: 'Dionysus Mansion', imagePath:'limassolRest/Dionysus Mansion.jpg', lat: 34.678925575501374, long: 33.03958286285314, city: 'Limassol',id: 1053, category: 'Restaurant, European Food', url: 'https://dionysusmansion.com/', description: 'Dionysus Mansion is a captivating dining experience nestled in the heart of Limassol, celebrated for its unparalleled fusion of culinary excellence and the mythological charm of Dionysus, the Greek god of wine and festivity. This enchanting restaurant is designed as a lavish homage to ancient Greek culture, offering a feast for the senses. Upon stepping inside, diners are transported to a world where the ambience blends rustic elegance with luxurious comfort, surrounded by walls adorned with classical art and lush, vine-draped terraces. The menu, a masterful blend of traditional Mediterranean flavors and modern culinary techniques, features dishes that are as divine as the deity it honors. Each meal is paired with an exquisite selection of wines, handpicked to complement the flavors and enhance the dining experience. Dionysus Mansion is not just a meal; it\'s a journey into a realm of gastronomic delight and cultural richness, making it a must-visit destination for those seeking to indulge in the art of fine dining (photo from e-table).' ),
    Place(name: 'Jam Limassol',id: 1054, imagePath: 'limassolRest/Jam Limassol.jpg', lat:34.67279623822456, long:33.04346313830094 , category: 'Brunch', city: 'Limassol', url: 'https://www.facebook.com/jamlimassol/', description: 'Jam in Limassol also refers to a trendy and beloved brunch spot, known for its vibrant atmosphere and innovative culinary delights. Nestled in the bustling heart of Limassol, this eatery has quickly become a hotspot for locals and tourists alike, eager to indulge in its unique twist on the traditional brunch experience. Imagine a place where the essence of a laid-back Mediterranean lifestyle meets a modern, eclectic flair, creating a dining ambiance that\'s both cozy and exhilarating.The menu at Jam is a testament to creativity and quality, featuring an array of dishes that blend local ingredients with international influences, ensuring there\'s something to tantalize every palate. From savory classics reimagined with a twist, like eggs benedict served on freshly baked artisanal bread, to sweet delights such as pancakes topped with homemade compotes and a sprinkle of edible flowers, each dish is a work of art. (photo from Check In Cyprus).')
