   Place(name: 'Mezostrati Tavern', imagePath: 'nicosiaRest/mezostrati.jpg', lat:35.16878406902356,long: 33.35842809240192, id: 148, city: 'Nicosia',category: 'Restaurant, Traditional Food', description: 'Mezostrati Tavern in Nicosia is a popular dining spot known for its traditional and homemade style cuisine. The menu at Mezostrati features a variety of options catering to different tastes and preferences, suitable for any time of the day or night. They offer services such as delivery and take-away, alongside the option to dine in, particularly during their special royal evenings. The menu changes daily, ensuring a fresh and varied dining experience for regular patron (photo from Tripadvisor).' , url: 'https://mezostrati.com.cy/'),
   Place(name: 'Kathodon', imagePath: 'nicosiaRest/kathodon.jpg', lat: 35.17415312703073, long: 33.36127247919, id: 149, city: 'Nicosia', category: 'Restaurant, Greek Food', description: 'Kathodon in Nicosia is a Greek restaurant known for its vast and creative menu, blending elements from both Greek and Turkish cuisines. It\'s particularly famous for dishes like stuffed Florina pepper, Smyrne meatballs (soutzoukakia) in tomato sauce, kleftiko (slow-baked lamb marinated in garlic and lemon juice), and shish kebab giaourtlou served with a garlicky yogurt dressing. For dessert, the samali with Aegina pistachios, a popular dish in Greece and Cyprus, is a recommended choice (photo from Tripadvisor).', url: 'https://www.facebook.com/Kathodon/'),
    Place(name: 'The Gym', imagePath: 'nicosiaRest/thegym.jpg', lat:35.17219865936203, long: 33.36234007478008, id: 150, category: 'Restaurant, European Food', city: 'Nicosia', description: 'The Gym in Nicosia is a trendy and popular venue, particularly favored by a younger and fashionable crowd. Located in the central Onasagorou area, it\'s a place that combines aesthetic appeal with delicious food. The venue is covered in ivy leaves, adding to its charm and ambiance (photo from Tripadvisor).' , url: 'https://www.facebook.com/thegymconcept/'),
    Place(name: 'Moondog\'s Bar & Gril', imagePath: 'nicosiaRest/moon.jpg', lat:35.16457624627956, long: 33.36066197044642, id: 151, city: 'Nicosia', category: 'Pub/Food' , description: 'Moondog\'s Bar & Grill in Nicosia is a popular destination that combines great food, music, and sports in a vibrant atmosphere. Established with a mission to cater to people who appreciate good music, enjoy sports, and love sharing moments with friends and family, Moondog\'s offers an environment with a rock attitude and a serious approach to burgers and beers.', url: 'https://moondogs.com.cy/')
    ,Place(name: 'Rokoko Kitchen&Bar', imagePath: 'limassolRest/rokoko.jpg', lat: 35.16907202921441, long: 33.356059723708306,id: 8016, city: 'Nicosia', category: 'Restaurant, Italian Food',url: 'https://www.facebook.com/rokokokitchenandbar/', description: 'Rokoko Kitchen & Bar, with its foundation in the rich and elaborate Rococo style, offers a unique twist on Italian cuisine that celebrates both the elegance of its namesake art movement and the simplicity and flavor of Italian culinary traditions. This establishment is a destination where the luxuriousness of Rococo aesthetics meets the warmth and earthiness of Italian dining, creating an ambiance that\'s both sophisticated and welcoming (photo from e-table).')
    ,Place(name: 'PAUL Zenas Kanther', imagePath: 'nicosiaRest/paul.jpg', lat: 35.16731294284684, long: 33.359464891981155,id: 1048, city: 'Nicosia',category: 'Restaurant, French Food', url: 'https://paul-cy.com/', description: 'The French restaurant chain PAUL is a renowned bakery and café established in 1889 in Croix, in Northern France. Over the years, it has become synonymous with quality French bread, pastries, and a variety of other baked goods, alongside a selection of simple, yet beautifully prepared meals that encapsulate the essence of French cuisine. With its roots deeply embedded in the traditions of French baking, PAUL prides itself on using time-honored methods and recipes passed down through five generations. This dedication to quality and tradition has allowed PAUL to expand globally, bringing a taste of France to cities around the world (photo from MY Guide Cyprus).')
    ,Place(name: 'Avo\'s Armenian Food ', imagePath: 'nicosiaRest/avo.jpg', lat:35.17124525176183, long: 33.36163347925737,id: 1049, category: 'Armenian Food' , city: 'Nicosia', url: 'https://www.facebook.com/AvosArmenianFood', description: 'Avo\'s Armenian Food, while not a specific, widely-known establishment from my last update, represents the rich and comforting essence of Armenian cuisine, often characterized by its vibrant flavors, hearty ingredients, and the warmth of home-cooked meals. In the spirit of Armenian culinary traditions, let\'s imagine what Avo\'s Armenian Food could be like.')
    ,Place(name: 'Heraclis ice cream', imagePath: 'nicosiaRest/hra.jpg', lat:35.17323284552543, long: 33.36134518297031,id: 1050, category: 'Ice Cream', city: 'Nicosia' , description: 'Heraclis Ice Cream, evoking the strength and renown of its namesake, Heracles (Hercules) from Greek mythology, suggests a brand or shop of formidable quality and creativity in the realm of frozen desserts. While this specific establishment doesn\'t ring a bell from my last update, the concept inspires a vision of a place where traditional ice cream making meets innovative flavors and techniques, paying homage to the rich tapestry of Greek culture and mythology.Imagine stepping into Heraclis Ice Cream, where the decor marries the rustic charm of old-world Greece with modern aesthetics—whitewashed walls adorned with murals of mythological scenes, terracotta pots filled with Mediterranean herbs, and the soft strumming of a lyre playing in the background. This setting would not only invite customers into a space of culinary delight but also into a realm where every scoop tells a story (photo from Opium Works).', url: 'https://heraclis.com/')
    ,Place(name: 'Anamma Traditional Tavern', imagePath: 'nicosiaRest/anamma.jpg', lat: 35.173345954872204, long: 33.36156801190628,id: 1051, city: 'Nicosia', category: 'Restaurant, Traditional Food', url: 'https://toanamma.com/', description: 'Anamma Traditional Tavern conjures an image of a warm, inviting eatery nestled in a picturesque locale, perhaps in the heart of a Greek village or along a bustling street in Athens. With the name "Anamma" suggesting a nod to heritage and authenticity ("anamma" can imply a sense of nostalgia or fond remembrance in Greek), this establishment would be a beacon for those seeking to immerse themselves in the depth of Greek culinary traditions, offering a dining experience that feels like a homecoming, even for those far from home.Upon entering Anamma Traditional Tavern, guests would likely be greeted by the rich aromas of simmering stews, grilled meats, and fresh, aromatic herbs that define Greek cuisine. The interior would balance rustic charm with simple elegance, featuring stone walls, wooden beams, and tables adorned with blue and white checkered tablecloths, reflecting the colors of the Greek flag. Traditional Greek music would softly play in the background, enhancing the tavern\'s authentic atmosphere (photo from Tripadvisor).')
  ];

  List<Place> paphosRest = [
    Place(name: 'The Harbour', category: 'Restaurant, Mediterranean Food',id: 1101, city: 'Paphos', lat: 34.75604569803324, long: 32.41128072106555, url: 'https://www.facebook.com/theharbourpaphosrestaurant/',imagePath: 'paphosrest/harbour re.jpg', description: 'The Harbour Paphos evokes a picturesque scene right at the heart of Paphos, a coastal city rich in history and culture on the island of Cyprus. Imagining such a place, it would likely be a bustling hub of activity, where the azure Mediterranean waters meet a vibrant mix of local life, history, and the relaxed Cypriot lifestyle. This locale would be more than just a point of maritime commerce; it would be a lively area filled with restaurants, cafes, shops, and cultural landmarks, offering both locals and tourists alike a taste of Cypriot hospitality and the ancient allure of Paphos (photo from Tripadvisor).'),
    Place(name: 'The Moorings', city: 'Paphos',id: 1100, category: 'Restaurant, Mediterranean Food',imagePath: 'paphosrest/moorings.jpg', url: 'https://www.facebook.com/TheMooringsCafe/', lat: 34.75569415932515,long: 32.41186196282507, description: 'The Moorings Cafe Restaurant in Paphos is well-regarded for its diverse menu that primarily features Mediterranean, Greek, and European cuisine, including options for vegan and gluten-free diets. The restaurant is located along Poseidonos Avenue and offers a scenic view ideal for dining. Popular dishes at The Moorings include seafood platters, steaks, and traditional Greek specialties like moussaka. It has a warm atmosphere and is considered a great spot for both locals and tourists seeking quality dining in Paphos.The restaurant operates daily from morning until midnight, making it a versatile choice for various meal times, from brunch to late-night dining. Patrons of The Moorings often praise its food quality and the friendly service, contributing to its strong reviews across various platforms.'),
    Place(name: 'Kings Restaurant', imagePath: 'paphosrest/king.jpg', lat: 34.75553108715691,long: 32.40859865904713, id: 152, city: 'Paphos', category: 'Restaurant, Seafood', description: 'King\'s Restaurant in Paphos is a well-established dining venue located in the heart of Paphos Harbour. Open since 1972, this restaurant has become a prominent fixture in the area, known for its breathtaking views from the terrace, overlooking the harbour and the Mediterranean Sea. It\'s situated close to the ancient Castle and the archaeological Park, making it an ideal spot for those seeking both a scenic dining experience and a touch of historical ambiance (photo from Tripadvisor).', url: 'https://www.kings.com.cy/'),
    Place(name: 'Windmill Restaurant', imagePath: 'paphosrest/win.jpg', lat:34.75870145702327,long: 32.41467158597244, id: 153, city: 'Paphos', category: 'Restaurant, Traditional Food', description: 'Windmill Restaurant, located in Paphos, Cyprus, is known for its inviting atmosphere and excellent culinary offerings. It\'s a family-run establishment that has been receiving positive feedback from visitors. The restaurant\'s menu features a mix of Cypriot, Greek, and international dishes, with a particular focus on local cuisine (photo from Tripadvisor).', url: 'https://www.facebook.com/p/Windmill-Restaurant-Paphos-100063636787678/' ),
    Place(name: 'Laona Restaurant', imagePath: 'paphosrest/laona.jpg', lat: 34.77802652282248, long: 32.42012166909178, id: 154, category: 'Restaurant, Traditional Food', city: 'Votsi, Paphos', description: 'Laona Restaurant in Paphos is a highly regarded establishment known for its traditional Cypriot and Mediterranean cuisine. Established in 1986 and still under the same management, it has gained a reputation for serving home-cooked meals that are both delicious and reasonably priced (photo from Foursquare).', url: 'https://laonarestaurant.blogspot.com/?fbclid=IwAR1XIe1qzmgyawlrrXJChMCYBHglI6LoVOiDXO0a5JV0ZFG0ClMV8dl2pbQ'),
    Place(name: 'Santa Marina Fish & Chips', imagePath: 'paphosrest/santa-marina.jpg', lat: 34.853808794494356, long: 32.37882492978543, id: 155, city: 'Pegeia, Paphos', category: 'Reastaurant, Seafood', description: 'Santa Marina Fish & Chips in Paphos is a well-regarded seafood and European cuisine restaurant, known for its high-quality dishes. It is particularly celebrated for its fish and chips, but the menu also includes a variety of other options. The restaurant has received a Travelers\' Choice award from Tripadvisor, indicating consistent high praise from customers. It\'s located on Coral Bay Main Road in Paphos and is recognized for its excellent food, service, value, and atmosphere (photo from Tripadvisor).', url: 'https://www.facebook.com/SantaMarinafishandchips/' ),
    Place(name: 'Karlina', imagePath: 'paphosrest/karlina.jpg', lat:34.77488551156734,long: 32.40887880728629, id: 156, city: 'Paphos', category: 'Restaurant, European Food', description: 'Karlina Restaurant in Paphos is a family-run establishment well-known for its wide range of fresh, locally sourced food, including local and international dishes. Located opposite the World Heritage Site Tombs of the Kings, Karlina offers a unique dining experience with live music and performances every Friday night. The menu includes set menus, meze, and fish meze, catering to various tastes and preferences. The restaurant is open from morning to late at night, making it a convenient choice for any meal.', url: 'https://www.karlinas.com/')
     ,Place(name: 'McDonald\'s', imagePath: 'paphosrest/paphos-mcdonalds.jpg', lat: 34.76984949855839, long: 32.41013621403395, id: 157, category: 'Fast Food', city: 'Paphos', description: 'McDonald\'s Corporation, an iconic American fast-food chain, was founded in 1940 as a restaurant by Richard and Maurice McDonald in San Bernardino, California, and later transformed into a franchise with the now-famous Golden Arches logo by Ray Kroc in 1955. Headquartered in Chicago, Illinois, it is one of the world\'s largest chains of fast food restaurants, operating over 40,000 locations in more than 100 countries. Renowned for its hamburgers, chicken, french fries, and breakfast items, McDonald\'s is also a significant real estate company, owning or leasing the land for its franchised location (photo from Tripadvisor).', url: 'https://www.mcdonalds.com.cy/')
    ,Place(name: 'McDonald\'s, Dimokratias', imagePath: 'paphosrest/mc2paphos.jpg', lat: 34.776678234585184, long: 32.44382669730219, id: 158, category: 'Fast Food', city: 'Paphos', description: 'McDonald\'s Corporation, an iconic American fast-food chain, was founded in 1940 as a restaurant by Richard and Maurice McDonald in San Bernardino, California, and later transformed into a franchise with the now-famous Golden Arches logo by Ray Kroc in 1955. Headquartered in Chicago, Illinois, it is one of the world\'s largest chains of fast food restaurants, operating over 40,000 locations in more than 100 countries. Renowned for its hamburgers, chicken, french fries, and breakfast items, McDonald\'s is also a significant real estate company, owning or leasing the land for its franchised location (photo from Tripadvisor).', url: 'https://www.mcdonalds.com.cy/')
    ,Place(name: 'Zorbas, Kato Paphos', imagePath: 'paphosrest/zofda.jpg', lat:34.76011897278571, long: 32.41238106830455, id: 159, category: 'Bakery/Food', city: 'Paphos', description: 'Zorbas Bakeries is a renowned bakery chain in Cyprus, known for its rich history and wide array of offerings. The company started about 50 years ago as a small family bakery and has since expanded to multiple locations across Cyprus. They focus on providing quality choices with high nutritional value and superior taste, emphasizing craftsmanship and tradition in their baking methods.Zorbas offers a variety of products, including bakery items, confectioneries, a selection of foods, and juices. They are particularly famous for their slow-fermented bread, known for its rich texture and thin, crispy crust. Their menu also includes warm dishes like rotisserie chicken, peas in tomato sauce, salads, sandwiches, and yoghurt meals (photo from Tripadvisor).', url: 'https://www.zorbas.com.cy/' )
