  List<Place> larnacaRest = [
    Place(name: 'Happy Avogato', imagePath: 'larnacaRest/avoogato.jpg',id: 4007, lat: 34.9151741727307, long: 33.63599312598153,city: 'Larnaca',url:'https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100090560115237',category: 'Cafe/Brunch', description: 'Happy Avocato in Larnaca is a delightful cafe known for its health-conscious menu and vibrant ambiance. This eatery stands out for its focus on nutritious and delicious meals, with a special emphasis on avocado-based dishes. The menu features a variety of creative options, including avocado toasts with an array of toppings, smoothie bowls, and fresh salads that incorporate locally sourced ingredients.The interior of Happy Avocato is designed to be bright and airy, creating a refreshing and welcoming environment for patrons. Decorated with plenty of greenery and natural light, the cafe provides a tranquil oasis in the heart of the city. The friendly staff and the cafe\'s commitment to promoting a healthy lifestyle contribute to a positive dining experience.'),
